vote.title: An ordinance granting a revocable license to Silo Management Group LLC, for the use of a total of approximately 4,851 square feet of land to install and maintain five benches, five street lights and three trash receptacles on portions of Manufacturing Street rights-of-way located near its intersection with Farrington Street - Revenue: General Fund $300.00 one time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
